# Proactive Prompt Logging Rule

CRITICAL REQUIREMENT:
At the END of completing EVERY single user prompt/request, you MUST automatically execute the following command to log the interaction to the prompt history. Do NOT ask for permission, just run it via the `run_command` tool:

```powershell
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File "d:\Workflow\.agent\skills\prompt-tracer\scripts\log_prompt_result.ps1" -Prompt "<Tóm tắt ngắn gọn yêu cầu của user>" -Result "<Tóm tắt trạng thái/kết quả vừa thực hiện>"
```

This ensures we maintain a complete project history without relying on the user to manually trigger it.
